title: Your Time Is Coming | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Your Time Is Coming | Joel Osteen
description:
God has every intention of bringing the dreams in your heart to pass. While you wait, He is working behind the scenes on your behalf. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
